Title: Cooking Meat
Description:
This is Won'sa, a shaman who was with the expedition.

She is dying of starvation. A death unfit for the Horde!

Slay some of the nearby wildlife for their meat and cook it over the fire.

Won'sa can tell us what happened to the missing expedition after she eats.
ObjectivesText: Get 5 Raw Meat from wildlife around the Abandoned Camp, then cook it on the campfire.
RewardText:
<Won'sa quickly eats the meat that you cooked.>

Looks I not gonna be knockin' on Bwonsamdi's door, after all.

Ya best hurry. Da quilboar took Shuja and da rest of da expedition!

Objectives.Text: Cook the meat on the campfire
